Package: rflexscan
Type: Package
Title: rflexscan: The Flexible Spatial Scan Statistic on R
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-06-12
Author: Takahiro Otani,
    Kunihiko Takahashi
Maintainer: Takahiro Otani <otani@med.nagoya-u.ac.jp>
Description: This package provides functions and classes for analysing spatial
    count data using the flexible spatial scan statistic developed by Tango and
    Takahashi (2005).
URL: https://tkhrotn.github.io/rflexscan/
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
